References: jsc#PED-13979 jsc#PED-14039 jsc#PED-14046 jsc#PED-14211 jsc#PED-14333 jsc#PED-14487 jsc#PED-14488 jsc#PED-14497 jsc#PED-14499

Wire xe_bo_move to GPU SVM migration via new helper xe_svm_bo_evict.

V2: - Use xe_svm_bo_evict
 - Drop bo->range
V3: - Kernel doc (Thomas)
V4: - Add missing xe_bo.c code
V5: - Add XE_BO_FLAG_CPU_ADDR_MIRROR flag in this patch (Thomas)
 - Add message on eviction failure
V6: - Only compile if CONFIG_DRM_GPUSVM selected (CI, Lucas)

Signed-off-by: Matthew Brost <matthew.brost@intel.com>
Reviewed-by: Thomas Hellstr√∂m <thomas.hellstrom@linux.intel.com>
